13:11.413 --> 13:12.597
And then what?

13:12.850 --> 13:15.193
- We didn't do anything wrong.
- Yes, we did.

13:15.511 --> 13:17.774
We didn't tell them, we
didn't give them a chance.

13:18.653 --> 13:20.370
Chance to what?

13:20.836 --> 13:22.338
Not adopt me.

13:22.374 --> 13:24.616
- Callie, they wouldn't have...
- We don't know that.

13:24.639 --> 13:27.019
They still can. They
can reverse my adoption.

13:27.041 --> 13:28.562
I looked into it. They can do it.

13:28.618 --> 13:31.318
You have to stop thinking
that nobody wants you.

13:31.438 --> 13:33.316
- This is different.
- No, it's not.

13:33.368 --> 13:35.323
