15:46.743 --> 15:49.101
And it started snow outside for real.

15:49.136 --> 15:50.721
San Diego, California.

15:52.663 --> 15:54.129
You think it was like a sign?

15:55.965 --> 15:57.475
I, uh...

15:57.741 --> 15:59.063
I like to think it was Frank

15:59.081 --> 16:01.847
