and forgave me, too, you know?

16:05.687 --> 16:08.974
I'm sorry you've had so
much loss in your young life.

16:10.734 --> 16:12.325
I really am.

16:14.457 --> 16:16.554
I love you, you know that.

16:17.115 --> 16:18.469
And I love you, too.

16:18.833 --> 16:21.297
Okay, get some sleep, baby.

