17:42.083 --> 17:44.752
Sure as hell won't ever do that again.

17:45.124 --> 17:48.357
- Is that fair?
- Yeah, I think so.

17:48.579 --> 17:50.355
Honey, we're still a family.

17:50.357 --> 17:52.038
