17:54.328 --> 17:57.246
Well, we can't pretend
like it didn't happen, yeah?

17:57.265 --> 17:58.525
Honey, it's not happening now.

17:58.531 --> 18:01.561
- Are you sure about that?
- I am, yes. I am.

18:04.894 --> 18:06.205
(sighs) Well...

18:08.878 --> 18:10.828
