18:10.949 --> 18:12.244
So it's different.

18:12.571 --> 18:15.234
We'll figure it out like
we do everything else.

18:16.250 --> 18:19.640
But none of the other kids need to know.

18:20.035 --> 18:22.561
In fact, I think it's
important that they don't ever.

18:22.682 --> 18:25.057
Well, I agree with you on that.

18:33.660 --> 18:35.381
Mariana: Are you awake?

18:38.323 --> 18:39.404
Yeah.

18:54.034 --> 18:55.203
Is it true?

19:05.099 --> 19:06.356
