19:07.845 --> 19:09.428
Up in Idyllwild.

19:10.644 --> 19:12.604
You and Brandon...

19:14.384 --> 19:15.641
Yeah.

19:27.665 --> 19:28.664
Anything?

19:28.700 --> 19:30.108
I've had a few calls from people who think

19:30.134 --> 19:31.962
