19:31.970 --> 19:32.984
Oh, that's good.

19:33.038 --> 19:34.614
You think we maybe can relax a little now?

19:34.663 --> 19:36.894
Well, I think if he
hasn't shown up by now,

19:36.909 --> 19:37.907
