Does someone else have it?

19:57.846 --> 19:59.813
(sighs) The hell?

20:15.012 --> 20:16.577
- Hey, Momma?
- Yeah.

20:16.698 --> 20:18.818
Do you think we could find
out where Jack's buried?

20:19.471 --> 20:21.392
I'm sure we could.

20:21.511 --> 20:23.085
Do you want to visit his grave?

20:23.622 --> 20:24.770
I think so.

20:24.806 --> 20:27.113
I remember Mom saying something
about him having an aunt.

20:27.130 --> 20:29.252
- I can try to find her phone number.
- Thanks.

20:29.285 --> 20:30.789
So, apparently Brandon got up this morning

20:30.807 --> 20:33.786
to go help Cortney move after I
distinctly forbade him from doing so.

20:33.813 --> 20:35.596
Wait, forbade?

20:35.609 --> 20:36.633
What are you doing?

20:36.681 --> 20:38.948
