gonna have to drive you.

20:55.871 --> 20:56.885
I can do it.

20:57.044 --> 20:57.921
Awesome.

20:57.923 --> 20:59.688
So we're safe now?

20:59.881 --> 21:01.757
We all just have to stay alert, please.

21:01.771 --> 21:03.025
No one goes out alone

21:03.041 --> 21:05.184
and make sure that the
doors are locked always.

21:05.713 --> 21:06.614
Jude: Okay, but...

21:06.733 --> 21:09.027
