our phones and computers back?

21:10.630 --> 21:12.113
Soon, love. Soon.

21:32.057 --> 21:33.082
(gasps)

21:33.131 --> 21:35.451
Sorry, um, just grabbing my toothbrush.

21:35.477 --> 21:36.576
I can go downstairs.

21:36.695 --> 21:37.894
It's okay.

21:40.554 --> 21:42.949
So, you haven't said two
words to me since I told you.

21:45.800 --> 21:48.792
