22:04.819 --> 22:06.329
I didn't mean to hurt anyone.

22:06.775 --> 22:08.411
And it's totally over.

22:08.692 --> 22:11.282
- What did Moms say?
- Haven't yet.

22:12.847 --> 22:14.763
Well, at least we don't
have to keep anymore secrets.

22:14.816 --> 22:17.490
Some secrets should be kept.

22:20.423 --> 22:22.295
Justina can't get away
with what she's done.

22:22.321 --> 22:23.705
We have to fight back.

22:23.741 --> 22:25.115
How?

22:25.824 --> 22:27.626
There's got to be something.

22:29.884 --> 22:32.353
I, um... I took a picture of a check

22:32.472 --> 22:34.584
Arbiter made out to Justina.

22:34.635 --> 22:37.154
Well, that proves that she works for them.

22:37.558 --> 22:40.574
I mean, and it makes her
liable for Jack's death.

22:41.076 --> 22:43.671
