22:44.778 --> 22:46.863
It's not like we can just
post it on Fost and Found.

22:48.032 --> 22:49.602
Well, we can't, but...

22:50.726 --> 22:51.942
Justina can.

22:52.938 --> 22:54.294
(line ringing)

22:54.365 --> 22:55.323
Woman: Hello?

22:55.442 --> 22:57.759
Hi, is this Linda Dawson?

22:58.029 --> 22:59.157
Yes.

22:59.573 --> 23:02.544
Hi, my name is Lena Adams Foster, um,

23:02.663 --> 23:05.858
and my son, Jude, was friends
with your nephew, Jack.

23:08.049 --> 23:09.345
Hello?

23:09.770 --> 23:12.028
- I'm here.
- Oh, I'm sorry. Um...

23:13.240 --> 23:14.955
anyway,

23:15.759 --> 23:19.369
