23:42.953 --> 23:45.265
I don't know what they
done with him. I'm sorry.

23:45.529 --> 23:47.289
(dial tone)

23:53.932 --> 23:55.223
Honey?

24:00.536 --> 24:02.113
Honey, are you up there?

24:02.184 --> 24:03.496
- Yeah!
- Oh!

24:03.546 --> 24:05.371
Sorry, sorry.

24:05.490 --> 24:08.083
- Did you find anything?
- No.

24:09.765 --> 24:11.252
The rat traps are empty.

24:11.373 --> 24:12.586
There aren't any droppings.

24:12.608 --> 24:14.915
I mean, I guess it
could have been the wind.

24:15.036 --> 24:16.776
- Hey, can I ask you something?
- Yeah.

24:16.990 --> 24:18.525
Do you know what the coroner does

24:18.583 --> 24:20.006
with remains that aren't claimed?

24:20.040 --> 24:22.659
Well, after a certain time, they bury 'em.

24:22.711 --> 24:23.479
Where?

24:23.491 --> 24:25.028
Uh, I don't know,

24:25.483 --> 24:26.926
a mass grave somewhere.

24:27.598 --> 24:28.405
Why?

24:28.605 --> 24:30.866
Well, I was talking to
Jude about, you know,

24:30.919 --> 24:32.585
trying to find some place where...

24:34.625 --> 24:36.378
And here I thought moving wasn't fun.

24:36.410 --> 24:37.617
(chuckling)

24:38.993 --> 24:40.663
Well, now that we don't
have to worry about

24:40.676 --> 24:42.340
Eddie walking in on us.

24:42.461 --> 24:45.055
Yeah, now all we have to
do is worry about Mason.

24:47.720 --> 24:49.167
I... I didn't mean that in a bad way.

24:49.326 --> 24:50.282
I know.

24:50.535 --> 24:51.642
He's a great kid.

24:52.372 --> 24:54.731
So what's, uh, going on with you?

24:55.635 --> 24:56.790
What do you mean?

24:57.459 --> 24:59.469
Well, when we were having sex,

24:59.500 --> 25:01.974
